
### Offboarding Module - HTTP Testing


### OFF-001: Create Termination Request (HR Manager)
### Initiates termination reviews based on warnings and performance data
POST http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439011",
  "initiator": "hr",
  "reason": "Performance issues after multiple warnings",
  "hrComments": "All procedures followed, warnings documented",
  "terminationDate": "2025-12-31T00:00:00.000Z",
  "contractId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439012"
}

### Get All Termination Requests
GET http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests

### Get Termination Requests by Employee
GET http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests?employeeId=507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

### Get Termination Requests by Status
GET http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests?status=pending

### Get Termination Request by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests/507f1f77bcf86cd799439013

### Update Termination Request Status (Workflow Approval)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests/507f1f77bcf86cd799439013/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved",
  "hrComments": "Approved by HR Director"
}

### Delete Termination Request (Only if not approved)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/offboarding/termination-requests/507f1f77bcf86cd799439013

